data.description: Qualified buyers can finance this home now for 100% with special financing through lenders who offer CAFA Gold or through Hancock Whitney's 100% Financing MMCT Loan. Contact Listing agent for more information. Introducing your fabulous family oasis! This beautifully renovated, 3 bedroom 1.5 bath home is situated on a double corner lot and is the perfect place to settle down and create lasting memories. Enjoy the painted brick exterior with new shutters, beautiful new front door and new exterior lighting for added curb appeal. Once inside you'll be taken by the neutral color palette throughout the interior with new dual zone central heating and air, updated electricals, all-new lighting fixtures, soft-closing cabinets in the kitchen featuring quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances. Both bathrooms have been completely updated too! Gorgeous wood lament flooring adds warmth throughout while a huge family room features its own separate central heat/air system. And just wait till you step out onto your stylish patio - ideal for outdoor entertaining or simply relaxing on warm summer days! Don't miss this amazing opportunity to call this tranquil retreat home. Security system to stay. - schedule a showing today!
